refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public intSplObjectStorage::removeAll SplObjectStoragestorage
Remove objetos contidos em outro armazenamento do armazenamento atual.

&reftitle.parameters;




   storage



     O armazenamento contendo os elementos a serem removidos.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Exemplo de SplObjectStorage::removeAll


<?php
$o1 = new stdClass;
$o2 = new stdClass;
$a = new SplObjectStorage();
$a[$o1] = "foo";

$b = new SplObjectStorage();
$b[$o1] = "bar";
$b[$o2] = "gee";

var_dump(count($b));
$b->removeAll($a);
var_dump(count($b));
?>


    &example.outputs.similar;


int(2)
int(1)
